      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published blood pump CFD literature (Hariharan et al. 2011, Fraser et al. 2012). Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model is FDA-accepted approach. Model form uncertainty quantification deferred per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
