      "acceptanceCriteria": "Nominal input values sourced from literature or measurement; sensitivity analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Blood density 1060 kg/m³, viscosity 3.5 mPa·s, hemolysis model constants from Giersiepen et al. 1990. Impeller rotational speed from pump datasheet. Formal input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Single FDA GCBP geometry used; sample variability analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "FDA GCBP is a standardised reference geometry with negligible manufacturing variability. Test sample characterisation beyond geometry verification not required at MRL 2. Single pump unit used for all bench experiments."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
