      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Dimensional equivalency between simulation and experiment confirmed via Reynolds number matching; formal equivalency analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Reynolds numbers matched between CFD and PIV experiments to within 2% across all operating points. Non-dimensional equivalency of primary flow parameters confirmed. Detailed equivalency parameter analysis scoped out at MRL 2."
